data.description: Low Maintenance Acreage on a paved road just minutes from Spencer and you still get to enjoy the freedom of country living!  New siding, Roof, Windows, Quartz counter tops, Furnace & A/C. Camper hook up.  New interior doors throughout the home. This home offers 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and an extra space for whatever it may be man cave, gaming, or exercise room! 4 acres to the west of this property is also listed at an additional $79,000 lots of possibilities to make this acreage your own.
